# BuildKit reads this file because it sits next to the Dockerfile
# (<dockerfile>.dockerignore). It trims the NDN_Service_Framework build
# context: host build artifacts, cloned dependency trees, and release
# tarballs are rebuilt or unneeded inside the image.
#
# If you use the legacy builder (DOCKER_BUILDKIT=0), copy this file to
# .dockerignore at the root of the NDN_Service_Framework checkout instead.
.git
build
dependencies
RELEASE
results
**/__pycache__
**/*.pyc
.lock-waf*
